---
import Page from '@/layouts/astro/Page.astro';
---

<Page>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar rugby-navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">ClubRugby.ca</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="terms-hero py-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="terms-title mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-dark opacity-75 mb-0">
        Fair use. Clear expectations. No nonsense.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
          <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
            <p class="text-muted fst-italic mb-4">
              Last updated: May 31, 2025
            </p>

            <p>
              Welcome to <strong>ClubRugby.ca</strong>. By accessing or using this
              website, you agree to the following terms. If you do not agree with
              these terms, please do not use the site.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Purpose of the Site</h5>
            <p>
              ClubRugby.ca exists to make grassroots and club rugby more
              accessible by providing fixtures, results, standings, and related
              information sourced from official and trusted providers.
            </p>
            <p>
              The site is provided for informational purposes only and does not
              represent any official league, union, or governing body unless
              explicitly stated.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Accuracy of Information</h5>
            <p>
              We make every effort to ensure the information on this site is
              accurate and up to date. However, schedules, results, and standings
              may change or contain errors.
            </p>
            <p>
              ClubRugby.ca is not responsible for decisions made based on
              information displayed on the site. For official confirmations,
              please refer to your league or union directly.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Use of the Site</h5>
            <ul>
              <li>You may use this site for personal, non-commercial purposes</li>
              <li>You may not scrape, overload, or intentionally disrupt the site</li>
              <li>You may not attempt to access restricted systems or data</li>
              <li>You may not misuse the site in a way that violates applicable laws</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Intellectual Property</h5>
            <p>
              All original content, site design, and presentation are the
              property of ClubRugby.ca unless otherwise credited.
            </p>
            <p>
              Logos, team names, league names, and data belong to their respective
              owners and are used for identification and informational purposes
              only.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Third-Party Links & Services</h5>
            <p>
              This site may link to third-party websites or services. We are not
              responsible for the content, availability, or practices of those
              external sites.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Availability & Changes</h5>
            <p>
              We aim to keep the site available and functioning smoothly, but we
              do not guarantee uninterrupted access.
            </p>
            <p>
              Features, data sources, or site functionality may change at any
              time without notice as the project evolves.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Limitation of Liability</h5>
            <p>
              ClubRugby.ca is provided “as is” without warranties of any kind.
              To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are not liable for any
              damages arising from the use or inability to use this site.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Changes to These Terms</h5>
            <p>
              These terms may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be
              reflected on this page with an updated revision date.
            </p>

            <h5 class="section-heading">Contact</h5>
            <p>
              If you have questions about these terms, please reach out via our
              <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
            </p>

            <div class="alert alert-light border mt-5">
              <strong>Good faith use:</strong>  
              This site is built for the rugby community. Use it respectfully,
              and we’ll keep doing our best to make it better.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>

<style>
/* Navbar */
.rugby-navbar {
  background-color: #c8102e; /* rugby red */
}

.rugby-navbar .navbar-brand {
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Hero */
.terms-hero {
  background: #ffcc00; /* rugby yellow */
}

.terms-title {
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #000;
}

/* Sections */
.section-heading {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
</style>
